  <!-- Codes — QR / barcode / SVG raster engine (src/Codes/). Svg.Skia drags SkiaSharp 3.119.2 transitively;
       SkiaSharp.NativeAssets.Linux ships libSkiaSharp.so into any Linux publish (Docker also needs libfontconfig1).
